stonehorse.grit

Class Maps

  • java.lang.Object
    • stonehorse.grit.Maps

  • public class Maps
extends Object
    Creation of persistent Associative Map structures that accept null as ordinary valid key value. The maps are read only, while mutation is an expression and hence a new value. The maps may differ in implementation depending on content and size. Larger maps share structure withAt previous maps. All element, keys and values, are expected to be effectively immutable.
